=begin rakudoc

=TITLE Changelog

=SUBTITLE User-visible changes by release

=head1 Overview

This changelog follows the shape of Keep a Changelog, adapted to Rakudoc.
Versions use the C<META6.json> version number and release tags use the
C<release-x.y.z> convention.

=head1 0.0.4 - 2026-06-29

=head2 Added

=item C<givenroot $root { ... }> syntax for temporarily binding the active
query data root while evaluating navigation expressions.

=item A sigil-less C<root> term for query code that needs to refer to the
currently bound data root.

=item Type-object selectors for query navigation, allowing expressions such as
C<RakuAST::IntLiteral> and C<RakuAST::Call> to match nodes directly by type.

=item Focused tests for data-root binding, type-object selectors, table
foreign-key navigation with a bound data root, and RakuAST ancestor lookup.

=head2 Changed

=item Renamed the dynamic query origin concept to data root in the query slang
runtime API and documentation.

=item Updated table navigation examples to use C<givenroot> instead of the older
query-origin helper style.

=item Expanded the release process documentation with install verification,
clearer release step grouping, and explicit fez/GitHub verification steps.

=head2 Fixed

=item RakuAST ancestor navigation now falls back to origin-based parent lookup
when a node exposes a C<parent> method that returns C<Nil>.

=item Descendant navigation now treats type objects as explicit selectors
instead of ignoring them as non-path values.

=head1 0.0.3 - 2026-06-29

=head2 Added

=item RakuAST tree navigation support through C<Qwiratry::Tree::Navigator::RakuAST>.

=item A dedicated tree navigator namespace, registry, and base role under
C<Qwiratry::Tree::Navigator>.

=item Documentation for adding tree navigators and for the release process.

=head2 Changed

=item Moved tree navigator discovery and registration out of C<Qwiratry::Format>.
Formats now stay focused on parse and render implementations.

=item RakuAST navigation no longer appears as a navigator-only format. It now
lives under C<Qwiratry::Tree::Navigator::RakuAST>.

=item Transformer default traversal now treats navigator-backed roots, including
RakuAST roots, as trees instead of inline scalar values.

=head2 Fixed

=item Calling a transformer on a RakuAST root now walks descendant RakuAST nodes
without requiring an explicit descendant query iterator.

=head1 0.0.2 - 2026-06-24

=head2 Changed

=item Aligned operator precedence documentation with the implemented query
operators.

=head2 Fixed

=item Fixed local package installation behavior.

=head1 0.0.1 - 2026-06-24

=head2 Added

=item Initial public release of Qwiratry.

=item RakuAST-backed query operators and query slang for navigation, set,
map-reduce, relational, and IO-style query expressions.

=item Tree and table walker infrastructure with lazy C<QueryIterator> execution,
walker planning, strategy hooks, and traversal context support.

=item Transformer and mold infrastructure, including mold matching, C<make>,
C<NextMold>, wrapper hooks, ordering, traits, and tree rewrite support.

=item Table navigation support, schema discovery, ordered-row navigation, and
foreign-key style relationship traversal.

=item Format, location, and IO implementation factories and demo parse/render
formats.

=item Rakudoc documentation for the architecture, operators, extension points,
and required Raku support.

=head2 Changed

=item Renamed the original template terminology to molds across the transformer
system.

=item Reorganized modules into the current C<Qwiratry::Format>,
C<Qwiratry::Walker>, C<Qwiratry::Strategy>, C<Qwiratry::Transformer>, and
C<Qwiratry::Query> namespaces.

=item Converted service-style modules to singleton facade classes where
appropriate.

=head2 Fixed

=item Stabilized zef testing and test layout under C<t/>.

=item Fixed lazy set operators, relation row equality, topic binding, wrapper
collection, and iterator exhaustion behavior.

=item Improved mold diagnostics, exception placement, and package metadata.

=end rakudoc
